<node CREATED="1590776192593" ID="ID_910030188" MODIFIED="1634920155248" TEXT="Continuos Integration">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <b><em style="border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: italic; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 15px; border-right-width: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; font-weight: 400; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: inherit; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; text-transform: none; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal"><font color="rgb(36, 39, 41)" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif"><i>Continuous Integration</i></font></em></b><font color="rgb(36, 39, 41)" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif">&#160;is a strategy for how a developer can integrate code to the mainline continuously</font>
    </p>
    <p style="border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 15px; border-right-width: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; font-weight: 400; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: inherit; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; text-transform: none; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal">
      
    </p>
    <p style="border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 15px; border-right-width: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; font-weight: 400; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: inherit; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; text-transform: none; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal">
      <font size="2">You might claim that it's merely a branching strategy in your version control system. </font>
    </p>
    <p style="border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 15px; border-right-width: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; font-weight: 400; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: inherit; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; text-transform: none; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal">
      
    </p>
    <p style="border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 15px; border-right-width: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; font-weight: 400; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: inherit; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; text-transform: none; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal">
      <font size="2">It has to do with the size of the tasks you assign to a developer; </font>
    </p>
    <p style="border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 15px; border-right-width: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; font-weight: 400; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: inherit; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; text-transform: none; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal">
      <font size="2">If a task is estimated to take 4-5 man-days then the developer will have no incitement to deliver anything for the next 4-5 days, </font>
    </p>
    <p style="border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 15px; border-right-width: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; font-weight: 400; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: inherit; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; text-transform: none; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal">
      <font size="2">because he's not done with anything - yet. </font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1634919863958" ID="ID_1969793939" MODIFIED="1634920155248" TEXT="Continuos Delivery">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-style: normal; margin-top: 0px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 16px; border-right-width: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; font-weight: 400; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Source Sans Pro, Helvetica, Arial; color: rgb(55, 62, 63); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: 1.5; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; padding-left: 0px; text-transform: none; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.1px" charset="utf-8">
      This is a Software Development Process where the continuously integrated (CI) changes will be tested &amp; deployed continuously into a specific environment, generally through a manual release process, after all the quality checks are successful
    </p>
    <br class="Apple-interchange-newline" />
    
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1634919993224" ID="ID_609898333" MODIFIED="1634920143396" TEXT="Continuos Deployment">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(55, 62, 63)" size="16px" face="-apple-system, system-ui, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Source Sans Pro, Helvetica, Arial">A Software Development practice where the continuously integrated (CI) changes are deployed automatically into the target environment after all the quality checks are successful</font>
