<node CREATED="1634920582088" ID="ID_211689803" MODIFIED="1634927284845" TEXT="Job">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;head&gt;
    
    
  &lt;/head&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 1.6rem; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Source Sans Pro, Helvetica, Arial; color: rgb(55, 62, 63); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: 1.5; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px&quot; id=&quot;jenkins-job&quot; charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; class=&quot;ibpage-article&quot;&gt;
      &lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;A Job/Project is the fundamental unit of a logical work (like a 
      software build, an automation task, test execution, etc) using the 
      Jenkins automation server and other required plugins, configurations &amp;amp; 
      infrastructures. &lt;/font&gt;
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 1.6rem; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Source Sans Pro, Helvetica, Arial; color: rgb(55, 62, 63); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: 1.5; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px&quot; id=&quot;jenkins-job&quot; charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; class=&quot;ibpage-article&quot;&gt;
      
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;border-right-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; margin-top: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Source Sans Pro, Helvetica, Arial; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; font-size: 1.6rem; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(55, 62, 63); line-height: 1.5; border-left-style: none&quot;&gt;
      &lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Jobs can be of different types like - a freestyle project, a 
      multi-configuration project, a pipeline project, a multi-branch project, 
      etc. &lt;/font&gt;
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/article&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;
    &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;rgb(26, 61, 60)&quot; size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;-apple-system, system-ui, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Source Sans Pro, Helvetica, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;section id=&quot;what-is-jenkins-pipeline&quot; class=&quot;ibpage-article-header&quot; align=&quot;start&quot; size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 0px; text-indent: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-right: 0px; line-height: 1.5; border-left-style: none; display: block; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; text-transform: none; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.1px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;Apple-interchange-newline&quot;&gt;
    

