<node CREATED="1634920667358" ID="ID_1839406164" MODIFIED="1634926965115" TEXT="Pipeline">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;head&gt;
    
    
  &lt;/head&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 1.6rem; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Source Sans Pro, Helvetica, Arial; color: rgb(55, 62, 63); vertical-align: baseline; margin-right: 0px; line-height: 1.5; border-left-style: none; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px&quot; id=&quot;what-is-jenkins-pipeline&quot; charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; class=&quot;ibpage-article&quot;&gt;
      &lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;The pipeline is a special type of Jenkins job - simply a sequence of 
      steps controlled by a defined logic - which Orchestrates long-running 
      activities that can span across multiple build agents. It is suitable 
      for building pipelines (formerly known as workflows) and/or organizing 
      complex activities that cannot be easily achieved using a freestyle job. &lt;/font&gt;
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;border-right-style: none; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; margin-top: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Source Sans Pro, Helvetica, Arial; padding-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; font-size: 1.6rem; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border-right-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(55, 62, 63); line-height: 1.5; border-left-style: none&quot;&gt;
      
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/article&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;
    &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;rgb(26, 61, 60)&quot; size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;-apple-system, system-ui, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Source Sans Pro, Helvetica, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;section id=&quot;types-of-jenkins-popeline&quot; class=&quot;ibpage-article-header&quot; align=&quot;start&quot; size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;border-right-style: none; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 0px; text-indent: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom-style: none; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; line-height: 1.5; border-left-style: none; display: block; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; text-transform: none; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.1px&quot;&gt;
